HTC DROID DNA Shot Leaked, Cleanest One Yet
HTC DROID DNA Shot Leaked, Cleanest One Yet

Here we have another shot of the HTC DROID DNA, the 5″ 1080p HTC device destined for Verizon. However, this shot is special: it’s high quality and clear and looks like an official press shot. It’s a good looking photo of a fairly good looking device.
If you look closely, the date on the widget says December 7th. Could this be a release date? We know that
. Could the release date be a whole month away? That sounds bad but is entirely possible. Or it might just be a random date, we really don’t know.
HTC and Verizon are hosting an event on the 13th of November, and it’s probably for this device
